{"tid":1292702,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王美斯：美洲盃為巴西而設 賽會收咗錢！","createTime":"2019-07-07T12:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T00:07:46.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"adfbe0c7177ea1fdad5d9efdc77a0849ca09226d","tid":1292702,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"美斯：美洲盃為巴西而設 賽會收咗錢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhnRE8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhnRE8a.jpg&h=7c772397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯爭執紅牌被逐 阿根廷挫智利奪季軍<br />\n<br />\n美洲盃早前4強阿根廷大戰巴西，該仗阿古路曾於禁區內被侵犯，球證不單毫無表示，就連翻看VAR也不願，最終阿根廷以0:2出局。於季軍戰中，美斯和智利隊長加利美度爭執，美斯於沒有動手之下竟然領紅出場。阿根廷贏2:1奪季，賽後美斯並沒有出席頒獎禮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24LLKAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24LLKAa.jpg&h=820f8917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯表示：「毫無疑問，整個賽事、所有判決都是為巴西而設。我希望VAR小組和球球證，能於決賽中有正常的判決，令秘魯不必受到我們之苦，但我認為很難發生。我不想處身於賄賂的賽事當中，阿根廷上下根本沒必要在這裡受到不公平對待。我們本應入決賽，但判決沒有容許，賽會讓全球球迷，未能好好享受足球。今場我領紅，就是因為我早前批評巴西的後果。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm0jO1A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm0jO1A.jpg&h=62b3da53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a88d2b239290955bd4a4751dfc34214db1868096","tid":1292702,"uid":43785,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"球王美斯呀，你冷靜啲啦<br />\n諗清楚好唔好，6年搞4屆<br />\n美洲杯為你而設㗎， 唔係為巴西而設呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己唔爭氣贏唔到巴西唔好怪人好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都入到去季軍戰， 雖然收咗個紅牌但係都攞到季軍啦。<br />\n你話最尾羅殿軍就嘈姐，攞季軍算撚數啦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你再係咁肉酸亂咁賴，我哋班friend好冇面呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568aaa0b1a98ff23f990a68f370bc3d09be6bcb8","tid":1292702,"uid":53855,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯表示：「毫無疑問，整個賽事、所有判決都是為巴西而設。我希望VAR小組和球球證，能於決賽中有正常的判決，令秘魯不必受到我們之苦，但我認為很難發生。我不想處身於賄賂的賽事當中，阿根廷上下根本沒必要在這裡受到不公平對待。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們本應入決賽</span></strong>，但判決沒有容許，賽會讓全球球迷，未能好好享受足球。今場我領紅，就是因為我早前批評巴西的後果。」</span><br />\n<br />\n美斯玩政治真係好撚恐佈，佢忍到笑嗰度好嘢。"},{"pid":"604e3a52c698eb5fa966dd5f4fe1a0535e115a12","tid":1292702,"uid":43785,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"568aaa0b1a98ff23f990a68f370bc3d09be6bcb8","tid":1292702,"uid":53855,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯表示：「毫無疑問，整個賽事、所有判決都是為巴西而設。我希望VAR小組和球球證，能於決賽中有正常的判決，令秘魯不必受到我們之苦，但我認為很難發生。我不想處身於賄賂的賽事當中，阿根廷上下根本沒必要在這裡受到不公平對待。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們本應入決賽</span></strong>，但判決沒有容許，賽會讓全球球迷，未能好好享受足球。今場我領紅，就是因為我早前批評巴西的後果。」</span><br />\n<br />\n美斯玩政治真係好撚恐佈，佢忍到笑嗰度好嘢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"一單還一單呀嘛， 你講今場黑鳩你咪算囉<br />\n決賽又想話人哋上一場都黑鳩你<br />\n不如講埋歐聯嗰場利物浦都係黑鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋為咗你球王美斯搞咗咁多屆美洲盃。<br />\n你又唔係表現得好好， 你話你自己好好表現入咗好多球波都話啦。依家你入一球12碼炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行出嚟同人講話人哋黑你？<br />\n你咪贏咗場季軍戰羅， 你自己唔出嚟攞獎咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n望住球王美斯搞成咁，個心真係好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329888009a9f16dfdb68bb58cb3161a5b4da0865","tid":1292702,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"仲有呀，講到美洲杯為巴西而設， <br />\n點解智利對阿根廷又要黑鳩你呢？<br />\n<br />\n好心你啦，唔好搞到美洲盃冇曬認受性啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今屆美洲盃球王美斯表現真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喜歡熱愛足球嘅球王美斯去咗邊？<br />\n作為咁多年美斯球迷覺得好傷心"},{"pid":"5dd40d0fe974346cdcb3042edfce7e9c04eccbfe","tid":1292702,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"敢言 講出事實"},{"pid":"76bff916855be59b351139cf9097be754aa65033","tid":1292702,"uid":87394,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"賽會為左你搞咁多屆比你反咬一啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f034263f0c2b727ac827f4c77722e94826c3ee","tid":1292702,"uid":172226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"我不想處身於賄賂的賽事當中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n09開始個幾年歐聯係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞咩輸波又懶地硬又懶球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />